I was disappointed to the point of being disgusted at the commentary of Richard 
Simmons and Vicki Lawrence Schultz during coverage of Pasadena's Doo-Dah 
Parade. 
</P>
<P>
Where I come from, if a person doesn't have anything good to say, he should 
keep his yap shut. 
</P>
<P>
James A. Brackley, Fountain Valley 
