<HEADLINE>
<P>
WHERE IS MR. SMITH? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
As a registered, turned-off, almost election-ignoring voter, I got a breath of 
fresh air from "Where Is Mr. Smith?" It was wonderful to find that there are 
Americans who care about conditions in this country (including Brownstein and 
Easton), who have some power to change things. 
</P>
<P>
MARIAN C. DUFFETT 
</P>
<P>
