<TEXT>
<P>
I find Sinead O'Connor's courage and honesty inspiring ("Nothing Compares 2 Her 
Year," by Robert Hilburn, Dec. 16). But I'm puzzled about her regret for 
avoiding a potentially uncomfortable experience with "Saturday Night Live." 
</P>
<P>
