STATES; MOTION PICTURE INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES; TELEVISION INDUSTRY -- UNITED 
STATES; ELECTRONICS INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES; TECHNOLOGY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
