left, Sofia Coppola, Diane Keaton, Al Pacino, George Hamilton, John Savage, Don 
Novello, Andy Garcia and Talia Shire. EMILIO LARI; Photo, Al Pacino as Michael 
in "The Godfather" (1972), "The Godfather Part II" (1974) and "The Godfather 
