<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Boston Celtics said they have signed free agent Derek Smith, 29, an 
eight-year NBA veteran recovering from knee surgery. Smith has averaged nearly 
13 points a game in his career, including three seasons with the Clippers in 
San Diego and Los Angeles. 
</P>
</TEXT>
