<SUBJECT>
<P>
BASKETBALL PLAYERS -- CONTRACTS; FREE AGENTS (SPORTS); BOSTON CELTICS 
(BASKETBALL TEAM); SMITH, DEREK 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA122390-0131 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 326404 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 23, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
