<HEADLINE>
<P>
IN SEARCH OF ZORRO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I am researching the life of Guy Williams for a tribute book. 
</P>
<P>
Known around the world as the romantic masked rider, Zorro, he gave us a 
timeless rendition of a legend -- and thus, became a legend himself. 
</P>
<P>
If anyone has any information, anecdotes, letters, pictures (especially from 
1920s-'40s), or anything to relate, please contact me. 
</P>
<P>
ANTOINETTE G. LANE 
</P>
<P>
P.O. Box 675 
</P>
<P>
San Pedro, CA 90734 
</P>
