and other servicemen in the gulf. GARY AMBROSE / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Sgt. 
Walt Baldwin, second row far right, and shipmates before their deployment to 
the Persian Gulf. He was to have been home by Christmas. ; Photo, COLOR, Walt 
Baldwin writes to Jeannie on board the amphibious assault ship Okinawa. "The 
worst part is the waiting," he says. 
